id: The 'all' ontology for Foundations (FND), North American Extension is provided for convenience for FIBO users. This ontology does not add new assertions, but imports the Production (Released) ontologies that comprise the FIBO Foundations (FND) domain, including extensions related to postal addressing in the US and Canada.
